Sentencas: Ceramic foams made from a wide range of ceramic materials are being considered for a whole range of applications.
Titulo: Preparation of electrically conducting ceramic foams

Sentencas: A promising application is electrically conducting ceramic foam which acts as current collector and air distributor at the cathode or anode side of solid oxide fuel cells (SOFC).
Titulo: Preparation of electrically conducting ceramic foams

Sentencas: In this work we detail a manufacturing process for electrically conducting ceramic foam by the replication of polyurethane templates.
Titulo: Preparation of electrically conducting ceramic foams
